{"tid":2369899,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台學者讚黎智英挺身抗威權","createTime":"2021-01-17T14:13:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-17T14:13:43.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5952d84c807b065090e3f01a6838ef5e71a27542","tid":2369899,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T14:13:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210117/JKNHU2E3GJGMHIPWT342ZBPRZ4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210117%2FJKNHU2E3GJGMHIPWT342ZBPRZ4%2F&d=yNoj9Y4wDskJCdIfGyfDHFiy1AgKJyIubMvfhItfpFI%3D&h=e09bd1b3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210117%2FJKNHU2E3GJGMHIPWT342ZBPRZ4%2F&h=59abc76a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210117/JKNHU2E3GJGMHIPWT342ZBPRZ4/</a><br />\n<br />\n台學者讚黎智英挺身抗威權<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/naQ_v4ztuJTi8DA-p-S6gYzR-rA=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SDKNVWVCIJD7ZHJND5BONX2QDA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FnaQ_v4ztuJTi8DA-p-S6gYzR-rA%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSDKNVWVCIJD7ZHJND5BONX2QDA.jpg&h=9cea1cf0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■黎智英由懲教署人員押送到接見室。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】壹傳媒創辦人黎智英早前復遭還柙後，上周四由荔枝角收押所轉到高設防的赤柱監獄，至今被還柙第18日。民主黨創黨主席李柱銘、前主席何俊仁及黎智英女兒，昨分別到監獄探望。事件繼續惹國際關注，台灣政治學者吳介民形容黎在威權壓逼和暴力威脅下毫不妥協，「腰桿還是挺得非常直」，又認為《蘋果日報》作為最後民主陣地，一定要盡量「撐過去」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/1-PHhXIYPKhmizobf87RJX-ZbH0=/1172x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BMZ27X5WEBHYFASQBFKGWPAD4M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F1-PHhXIYPKhmizobf87RJX-ZbH0%3D%2F1172x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBMZ27X5WEBHYFASQBFKGWPAD4M.jpg&h=e2b9fc3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■李柱銘（右）偕何俊仁到赤柱監獄探望黎智英。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n李柱銘偕何俊仁探監<br />\n<br />\n昨早約10時，李柱銘偕何俊仁到達赤柱監獄，表示以律師身份探望黎智英。其間黎由三名懲教署人員押送到接見室，與李、何二人見面。至上午10時40分，黎智英女兒偕一名女親友到來探望，並帶備零食和梳洗消毒的日用品。李及何逗留至11時45分離開，指黎精神不俗。黎女和女親友亦於中午離開。<br />\n<br />\n台灣政治學者兼中研院社會學研究所研究員吳介民，接受台灣《蘋果新聞網》訪問時，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n吳相信，拘捕黎的另一目的是清洗香港《蘋果日報》，特別是在《港區國安法》實施後，很多香港媒體不斷被清洗、整肅，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/eKlkdi0rXEBVa_AdbGDZD18G_44=/545x545/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GXBAZZ3NABAGTKTAO34BGYQUKY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FeKlkdi0rXEBVa_AdbGDZD18G_44%3D%2F545x545%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGXBAZZ3NABAGTKTAO34BGYQUKY.jpg&h=80ef9dd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n吳介民"}]}